fields.name: ApnsCertificate
fields.description: Gets or sets the APNS certificate.

fields.name: AppId
fields.description:
Gets or sets the issuer (iss) registered claim key, whose value is
your 10-character Team ID, obtained from your developer account

fields.name: AppName
fields.description: Gets or sets the name of the application

fields.name: CertificateKey
fields.description: Gets or sets the certificate key.

fields.name: Endpoint
fields.description: Gets or sets the endpoint of this credential.

fields.name: KeyId
fields.description:
Gets or sets a 10-character key identifier (kid) key, obtained from
your developer account

fields.name: Thumbprint
fields.description: Gets or sets the APNS certificate Thumbprint

fields.name: Token
fields.description:
Gets or sets provider Authentication Token, obtained through your
developer account
